Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Doug LeMoine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm a design evangelist here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,at Apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be joined in a bit by Jake
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Behrens.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He and I have teamed up to work
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with Apple Watch developers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,around the world over the past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Helping them make their Apple
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch apps as awesome as
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're here today to share
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,what we've learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be here because you've
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.06,0:00:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,been developing for Apple Watch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.87,0:00:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're looking for some
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,inspiration and ways to improve
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,your app.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you might be here because
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:00:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you're new to the platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. You saw Monday's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.30,0:01:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,keynote, you heard about the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,improvements, and now you're
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.03,0:01:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,ready to get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got tips, ideas and advice
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that will be useful to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.83,0:01:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to begin by talking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.08,0:01:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,about planning, where to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.03,0:01:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, if you've already got an app
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,where to go next with your next
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.46,0:01:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,release.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to show practical
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,methods that you can use to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,define a great Watch app.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Jake is going to talk
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,about the implementation of a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,app on Apple Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But what he's really going to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,focus on is how you can learn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,from building.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to talk about how we
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,tested ideas and learned from
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the people who use our app since
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.69,0:01:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the initial launch of Apple
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.89,0:01:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, let's dive in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.77,0:01:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, believe it or not, it was
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,only 2 years ago that Apple
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.41,0:01:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch was unveiled to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and since then capabilities have
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,increased with each hardware and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,software release.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past year alone, the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:01:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,power and performance have
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:01:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,doubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And Apple Watch Series 2 extends
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,what you can do with the watch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,with built-in GPS and water
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,resistance up to 50 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This means it Watch apps can
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,track your workouts, when you go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,for a bike, ride, or a swim, or
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a run.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And some health and fitness apps
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,provide inspiration for the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,platform as a whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I want to walk through a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,couple of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweat, an app from Australia can
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,guide you through a variety of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.38,0:02:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,different exercises.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, these are 28-minute workouts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.68,0:02:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,with literally dozens of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And each of them has a helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,animation on the watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not sure how to do a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,particular movement, you can get
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,visual guidance right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Zepp helps you improve your
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,tennis swing by using a sensor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,mounted on the racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You might've seen this in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday's keynote.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But it gives you immediate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,feedback on your last serve in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,this case so you can adjust for
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can make a serve, look
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,at your wrist, you can see how
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:02:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,RunGo from Vancouver can give
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you turn by turn directions on a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,road or a trail run.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You simply load the route that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you want and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is voiceover, which is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,an accessibility feature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And the audio can play through
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the Watch speaker, or through
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bluetooth headphones that you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,can connect directly to the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what can we learn from the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,success of apps like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, in the past year,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,we've traveled around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've seen successful watch
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,apps, we've seen that successful
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,watch app development begins
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,with planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Which sounds obvious I imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But for Watch, the best way to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,begin planning is to be ruthless
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and focusing and to identify a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,single feature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A single job to do on Apple
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A single task to complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A single goal to achieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this could be an existing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,feature from your iOS app, or it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,could be something new that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,makes sense on the wrist and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that supplements what you do on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,iOS.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is an app called Night
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky, from the UK.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If I see something up in the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,sky, I can use the Night Sky app
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,on Apple Watch to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case, it actually starts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,with a notification that points
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,my way to the International
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Space Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's what the arrow is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a simple feature like this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,can provide a small, or even big
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,moment of delight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of delight, I can also
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,see if a new cat toy has brought
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,any new cats to my yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Neko Atsume from Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, are there any new
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Look at that little
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But to be honest I'm more of a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,dog person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is an awesome app.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do these apps do well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They reduce the scope of what
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,they try to do down to one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that makes sense on the wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Night Sky offers a way to answer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,one question, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Night Sky's iOS app does much,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Check out all the things you can
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can find constellations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can learn about stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can spend minutes or even
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,hours in here exploring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no menus in the watch
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,app.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no navigation at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than the cosmic navigation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,of course, that the app allows
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's things like this, in my
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,opinion, that really show what
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the platform can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, once you have your feature
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got some guidelines for
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,extending the UI and the UX of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,your app on the Watch platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so the UI's of great
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Watch experiences, have
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,three characteristics or
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,First, they're legible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning the text on the screen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is readable with sufficient
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,contrast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying this like it's
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,revolutionary, but it's actually
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,really simple and it's really
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,key.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Watch comp that you design
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,might look awesome on your 5K
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,iMac, but you need to see how it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,performs on the small screen of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the device itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it legible?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you read it in a glance?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In bright sunlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Great experiences, as we all
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,know, start with getting the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,little things right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, make sure that the text and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,graphics on your Watch face are
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,readable in the specific
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,conditions of watch use.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, number 2, they're concise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,To the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the information that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,matters, only the actions that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch experiences can be truly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,powerful when the Watch app has
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,tightly defined what it's trying
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to do, and then delivers it in a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,form that the user can grasp in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.19,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, they're timely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Chuckles ]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man, I have to wait for
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,groans and uncomfortable coughs
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In all seriousness, timely is
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,actually just the most direct
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,way of describing the Watch
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,being relevant in the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Both in a temporal sense and in
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,a situational sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're going to use this as a
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,checklist as we look through
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,some Apple Watch experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd encourage you to do the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,same when you plan and design
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,your apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's look at an
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,example.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It displays 3 simple elements on
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The type is big with good
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,contrast right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Legible. The elements are
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,informative, action oriented and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,optimized for one thing; request
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Concise. Also, the relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,between the elements is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got my location.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a 1 minute waiting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's timely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And notice that Lift is keeping
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the location area simple and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,glanceable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're also doing things behind
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the scenes to populate it with
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,things that users might
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,recognize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Favorites, previous places, or
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,just well-known places.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay let's look at another
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,example.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Major League Baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The team names are big, really
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,big.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For the most part legibility is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,about size on Apple Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wonder whether your type
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is big enough, it probably
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When the primary information is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,undeniably primary, you're
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,heading in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The relevant details with Major
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,League Baseball are concise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's pitchers and their
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,records.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, it's showing me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,only today's game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Timely. All right, now I want to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,talk about concise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is CBS News.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at the home view, which
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,shows headlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can simply scroll through and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.38,0:09:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,get caught up in a few seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How many headlines does it show?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually around 8 to 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's drill in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now we're in the article
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,view.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And once we get here, we can
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,quickly scan down through the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,article using the digital crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And pretty quickly I get to the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is actually just a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,synopsis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can continue reading on my
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,iPhone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Either by using Handoff or by
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,bookmarking it and saving it for
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's talk about what
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,they did well here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Big, bright text.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Concise. It doesn't necessarily
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,mean fits on one screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It can simply mean one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that a person cares about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, even though this experience
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,involves scrolling headlines and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,text it feels simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, timely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have access to the latest news
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in a super accessible form.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now that we talked about
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the UI of apps, I want to talk
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,about the other side of the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The person using your app.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to get
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,aspirational about the kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,experience that can be created
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,on Apple Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,On iPhone, we all know that apps
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,can help people get things done,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,answer questions and achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Watch, the goals are the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,same, but the parameters of the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,experience are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The screen is small.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the information needs to be
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,distributed in small chunks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Watch experiences involve
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,apps doing work on behalf of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Working in the background and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,emerging at the right time to be
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of like an expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who's smart about stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that I care about and leaps in
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to offer help when necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Like an engineer or a scientist,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,like mission control who helps
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,an astronaut navigate space, who
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,informs the astronaut when
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,decisions need to be made or
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,when new information is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,available.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Information that helps
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,navigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The status of the spacecraft,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,are the pod bay doors open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it time to jump to hyper
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how engineers behind the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,scenes assist astronauts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The scientist manages the flow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of information to the astronaut
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and gets her the information she
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,needs just in time in a concise
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and timely way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the good news is being
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,helpful in this way is not
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,rocket science.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrible joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take WWDC as an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You spent the last 3 days,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,surrounded by life forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You may know some of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them may know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have connections that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,neither of you even knew about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The iPhone helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There are various ways of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,organizing your life on iPhone;
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,contacts apps, social networks
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All of which are useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Apps like these typically
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,provide places that help people
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,begin looking for information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you want the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,information to come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You want these apps to be
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,proactive or predictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You want help remembering a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Or help revealing a connection
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,or a common interest that you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,might have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My point here is that the magic
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and delight of Apple Watch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,happens when your apps work on
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,behalf of your users to get them
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the information they need in the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And by doing this and still
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,trust that they will continue to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,do so in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when your app is legible,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,concise and timely your users
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,will feel a personal connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're going to add a fourth
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,quality of great Apple Watch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences, personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:12:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Being legible, concise and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,timely establishes that personal
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,connection with each individual
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,who uses your app.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing that they'll get the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,information they need when they
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Like an astronaut trust people
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,at mission control to pass along
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the right information at the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,right time, so that they can
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,stay focused on the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, we're going to travel back
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,down to earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to look at a quick
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,example.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Calendar. This is mission
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,control, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the big canvas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where you can survey the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,see what's going on for the next
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,week or month.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you've got all the dials
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and levers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can create calendars, create
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,meetings, move stuff around,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,tons of real estate, and tons of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As you move on the iPhone, the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,view narrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Well because this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,accurately reflects the scope of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,what you typically care about on
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,a mobile device.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can still navigate through
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,weeks and months, but you're
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,focused on the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Zooming in further, to the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Watch shows you the next
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,event.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You can scroll through events
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,over the day and into subsequent
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's optimized for the next
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, the calendar
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,complication.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I can keep track of where I
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,need to be by simply glancing at
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,my wrist and seeing it right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,there in the middle of my watch
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we've gone from mission
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,control to the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I've shown some different
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.18,0:14:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,components of Apple Watch, now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,let's walk through each one
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of these can be used to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,deliver information to your
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,users on Apple Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The three components of every
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And like they're shown here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,they're equally important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike other platforms, the app
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,is not necessarily the center of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,an experience on Apple Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There are complications which
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,are persistently displayed on
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the Watch face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a way for you to provide
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,ambient information or access to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,your app.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Notifications, which you're
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,probably already using on iOS,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll talk about what's
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,different on Apple Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, the app itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Important of course, but not
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,necessarily more so than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's start with the most
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,persistent element of the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The complication.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Information from your app on the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Complications are helpful when
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,they're continuously providing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,value to users.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what persistently provides
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,value?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, being relevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Being predictive, offering a
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,peek into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Showing progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, simply providing a launch
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,button for your app.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There are examples of each of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,these on the Watch face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,CARROT weather is immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,relevant to both here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It shows me the temperature and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,current atmospheric conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Night Sky shows me that Neptune
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an upcoming thing that I
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's the calendar
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,complication, letting me know
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,what I've got coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, Nike Run Club shows me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the miles I've logged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Incremental progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, as you saw on Monday, the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Siri face on watchOS4 brings
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,timely information to you from a
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,variety of places.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this face adapts, delivering
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,timely, concise information
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than requiring people to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,go and find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, so those are complications.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about notifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,On Apple Watch, notifications
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,briefly take over the UI
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,allowing people to fully engage
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This means that from the point
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,of view of the person using your
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,app a notification from your app
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is essentially your app.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This notification can be styled
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to look like you're app and it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,can deliver information and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,provide timey actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:16:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's look at an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Organizing a soccer game can be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to find a field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes that a big open space
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to play soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to find a time to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,play, coordinating schedules can
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,be complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to find players.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want the game to be fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the players need to be of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,roughly the same skill level.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, you need to collect
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,fees, sometimes for the field or
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is an app called
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Apitador.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It answers the question where
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and when can I play a pickup
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,soccer game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it shows me a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say I'm at the Apple
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,office in São Paulo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There tons of games going on
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I can create a profile for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,myself in iOS, including the way
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that I like to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's be honest, I have no
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,place in a pickup soccer game in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But let's go ahead and create a
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,profile anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As I start playing games, other
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,players can rate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I a good player?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I show up on time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:17:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I friendly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are organizing games,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.57,0:18:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,can see that and they can invite
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,me when they need a player like
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A "attacking midfielder" which
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is I guess what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when someone invites me to a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,game, I can see this invitation
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,appear as a notification.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case, a person who is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,organizing a game has reached
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,out to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a game on Friday at 7pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I can swipe down in the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,notification and see a quick map
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of where the game is, not far
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,from the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And super helpful actions that I
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,can tap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.29,0:18:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I can say, I'm in, or out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,or dismiss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's quickly evaluate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Super readable, uses their brand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,shade of green really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's soccer green.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Very legible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Super concise as well, all the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,information is there in a swipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pickup soccer, which can
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:18:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,be pretty spontaneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, getting a notification about
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,a game that might happen soon is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,also really helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that I can take
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,appropriate action directly from
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the notification is pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And receiving simple,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,informative notifications from
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,an app that I trust about
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.31,0:19:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,something that I love doing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.79,0:19:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,makes me feel pretty great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty amazing to be able
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to act immediately without
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,reaching into my pocket and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,pulling out my phone to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what I've really liked about
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,this is that they extended their
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,app to the wrist in a helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,delightful way that made sense
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,for what they do, organize
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,soccer games.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm much more likely to continue
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to engage with apps like this
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,when they reach out to me with
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,valuable information and give me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,easy ways to take action or make
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:19:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's notifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the app as I said, isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,necessarily the center of the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,experience on Apple Watch, but
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,obviously, it's important to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,consider what kind of experience
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you can provide in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Notifications and complications
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,can feel proactive and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,predictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Apps on the other hand are best
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,when they provide simple and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,direct actions, or tools, or
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,information.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an app called Elk, it's
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,from Singapore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a currency converter that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,uses simple gestures in the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,digital crown to quickly figure
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,out how expensive a thing is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to be clear, the question
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,they're answering this how much
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in this case, I'm in Canada,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm buying something, maple
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,syrup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,With a couple of swipes, there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,we go, we can swipe out some
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,decimal places and a couple of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,digital crowns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can have increment it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.06,0:21:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, one last tweak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems kind of expensive for
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,maple syrup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did they do well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they've allowed me to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.36,0:21:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,quickly calculate a price, and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,they've also kept it discrete,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it saves me the embarrassment of
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,not knowing that this is how
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,much it costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very simple to do this with
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,a couple of gestures, and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,they've also saved me some
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's evaluate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Big type, legible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All on one screen, concise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Helpful and discrete, timely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally trustworthy and helps me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,solve a real-world problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome. OK before I turn it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,over to Jake, I'm going to take
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you through a quick app planning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,exercise where we will put to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,use the things that we just saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're going to plan an app,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.42,0:21:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,from start to finish in just a
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:21:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,couple of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say Jake and I work for a
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,company called SailBoss.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that Apple Watch Series 2
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.06,0:22:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is water resistant with onboard
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,GPS, it seems like it's time to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,bring our iOS app to Apple
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I open up Sketch and I grab
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.26,0:22:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,an art board.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Start thinking about what we
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,could bring over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We worked on some cool graphs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.29,0:22:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and visualizations for the iOS
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.04,0:22:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,app.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It would really be a shame to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,not bring them over to Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.02,0:22:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This one shows wind with an
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.57,0:22:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,animated arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.96,0:22:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one shows swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This helps people understand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,whether the conditions on the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.93,0:22:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,water will be in their comfort
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, there's the temperature
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of the air and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.14,0:22:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, there are plenty of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,other metrics that determine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,good sailing conditions; tides,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.76,0:22:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and seasons, and whether Neptune
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is rising and setting, and so
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But at SailBoss we focused on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,these.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.80,0:22:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:22:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now we want to take these
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.40,0:23:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,graphs into a Watch UI.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, back to Sketch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.58,0:23:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if we can represent
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,all the metrics that matter to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.52,0:23:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,our users.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.04,0:23:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right I need to adapt the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,wind graphic a little bit to fit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.85,0:23:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I've strung it across the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.88,0:23:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,top, because it's the most
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,important.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's the swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's pretty small.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll put the air
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.53,0:23:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,temperature down at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.47,0:23:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't really fit in the water
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.16,0:23:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's like an iOS app but
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,miniaturized.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.25,0:23:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to evaluate this
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,against the four qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.49,0:23:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, is it readable?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.78,0:23:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's actually possible
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.63,0:23:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is readable in this room
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,on this massive screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But on the wrist, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.42,0:23:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not readable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We tried. It's just not readable
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.17,0:23:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,on Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.54,0:23:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it direct in answering the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.05,0:23:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,question should I go sailing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.88,0:23:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,today?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.73,0:23:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Graphs are nice and there's lots
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.74,0:24:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of information, but there's no
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.46,0:24:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,way to glance at this and answer
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.01,0:24:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.15,0:24:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, no. Is it timely?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean technically, I have the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.83,0:24:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,times listed across the top,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.98,0:24:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that doesn't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.10,0:24:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make the information
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,itself timely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.51,0:24:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.73,0:24:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In our little scenario, Jake and
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.69,0:24:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a lot of information
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.61,0:24:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,about the users who use our app.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.11,0:24:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We know what their preferences
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.41,0:24:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,are for their sailing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.36,0:24:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,conditions, but the UI is not
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.02,0:24:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,really making this clear at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.60,0:24:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, back to the drawing board.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.21,0:24:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We could just allow a chart or
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.95,0:24:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,graph to take over the entire
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.70,0:24:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.11,0:24:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind seems like the primary
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.88,0:24:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.24,0:24:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's start there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.42,0:24:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We can even add the title up in
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.05,0:24:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the status bar, that would help
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.18,0:24:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,with overall clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.78,0:24:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's test this out on a
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.02,0:24:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.56,0:24:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely more legible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.26,0:24:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, concise.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.55,0:24:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like it could be pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.71,0:24:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,helpful to have on the wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.33,0:24:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You launch the app and see the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.50,0:25:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,current wind conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.97,0:25:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, this gives me an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.53,0:25:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be helpful on the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.29,0:25:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,face of the Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.72,0:25:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A sailing complication.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.15,0:25:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a nice way to glance at
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.75,0:25:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the current wind conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.20,0:25:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's relevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.59,0:25:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's information about the here
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.92,0:25:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.96,0:25:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Persistent information that's
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.55,0:25:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.90,0:25:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're getting somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.71,0:25:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, not all apps have something
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.80,0:25:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,like this, but I think this one
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.56,0:25:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,does.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.49,0:25:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right let's go back into the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.62,0:25:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,app.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.72,0:25:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We could include other graphs as
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.19,0:25:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,additional pages, we can put
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.94,0:25:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,some page dots in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.14,0:25:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And then bring the other graphs
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.07,0:25:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.76,0:25:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,With watchOS4, you can even
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.60,0:25:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,launch the app on the second
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.24,0:25:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,page, put the wind there and
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.53,0:25:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that would mean temperature and
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.13,0:25:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,swell are both just one page
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.27,0:25:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,away from the most important
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.54,0:25:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,information.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.27,0:25:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to ask Jake about that
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.56,0:25:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,one, but I kind of like that
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.00,0:25:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.62,0:25:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it's complete, but it's
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.41,0:25:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,not concise.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.55,0:26:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take much longer than a
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.02,0:26:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,glance to see whether conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.86,0:26:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,were favorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.90,0:26:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'd have to be swiping
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.94,0:26:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,back and forth, and tracking the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.93,0:26:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.97,0:26:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We could highlight the type
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.67,0:26:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,range when conditions are
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.80,0:26:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,favorable, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.36,0:26:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's imagine that this is a
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.97,0:26:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,user's preferences announced as
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.00,0:26:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a primary visual element in the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.77,0:26:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,graphs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.23,0:26:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like it's getting
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.18,0:26:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,closer to being personal, but
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.15,0:26:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it's still not great.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.50,0:26:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have to do too much
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.51,0:26:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,swiping back and forth and
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.81,0:26:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,figuring out whether those
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.38,0:26:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,highlighted areas are going to
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.55,0:26:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,match up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.76,0:26:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's think about another
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.24,0:26:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,element of the Watch platform,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.98,0:26:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,notifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.99,0:26:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they could actually be
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.94,0:26:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,pretty helpful here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.38,0:26:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we could actually create
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.60,0:26:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,a pretty awesome experience with
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.12,0:26:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,these given that we know about
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.85,0:26:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the conditions that people
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.98,0:26:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,prefer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.21,0:26:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We could fire off a notification
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.46,0:26:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,when the wind, and temperature
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.44,0:26:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and swell all got into the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.35,0:26:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,comfort zone of a person using
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.52,0:26:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,our app.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.34,0:26:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to launch the Watch app
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.00,0:26:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and swipe from page to page.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.97,0:27:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,People can trust that SailBoss
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.43,0:27:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,will let them know when
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.50,0:27:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,conditions are awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.77,0:27:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, we could even include
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.06,0:27:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,some graphics to show that the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.37,0:27:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,wind is in their comfort zone,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.04,0:27:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,highlighted and vivid SailBoss
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.92,0:27:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,green.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.03,0:27:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And we could provide actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.19,0:27:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple stuff that could help us
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.75,0:27:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,tune future notifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.93,0:27:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This would help us learn more
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.03,0:27:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,about each person who taps each
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.21,0:27:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,one of these actions, and
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.05,0:27:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore provide even more
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.93,0:27:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,personalized information to them
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.46,0:27:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.66,0:27:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. In this example, we focused
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.19,0:27:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,on a single feature.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.46,0:27:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A single question.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.44,0:27:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've arrived at what I
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.03,0:27:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,think is a decent hypothesis for
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.78,0:27:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,what we should build.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.94,0:27:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I mean by planning
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.49,0:27:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,for Apple Watch, clearly
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.73,0:27:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,defining how your app will take
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.04,0:27:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,advantage of the small screen,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.37,0:27:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the context of use, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.28,0:27:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Watch platform components.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.00,0:27:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But, too much of anything is
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.38,0:27:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,unhealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.30,0:28:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to know how this lands
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.35,0:28:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with the people who you're your
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.40,0:28:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,app.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.04,0:28:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to see how people use,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.12,0:28:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,or don't use your feature.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.12,0:28:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What they love and what they
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.01,0:28:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.71,0:28:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm going to turn it over to
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.10,0:28:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake to walk you through a
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.91,0:28:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,real-life example of what we've
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.04,0:28:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,learned over the past three
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.20,0:28:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,versions of the WWDC app.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.52,0:28:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.67,0:28:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.61,0:28:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Jake Behrens, and I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.39,0:28:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the Apple Watch Technologies
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.84,0:28:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Evangelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.34,0:28:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, as well as being an
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.74,0:28:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,evangelist, I'm also an engineer
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.13,0:28:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,on the WWDC App.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.48,0:28:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,At Apple we're pretty secretive
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.64,0:28:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,about our development process.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.80,0:28:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But today I want to do something
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.13,0:28:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,different.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.20,0:28:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to pull back that curtain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.75,0:28:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and I want to give you a
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.04,0:28:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,behind-the-scenes look at how we
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.51,0:28:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,developed the WWDC app on
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.23,0:28:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,watchOS.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.43,0:28:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Version by version, over the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.52,0:29:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,last three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.81,0:29:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I want to share with you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.74,0:29:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,our experiences and our missteps
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.66,0:29:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.47,0:29:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In doing this, I'm hoping to
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.38,0:29:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,impart some things for you to
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.54,0:29:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,gain insight on and areas for
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.02,0:29:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you to stay mindful of as you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.31,0:29:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,develop your own Watch apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.10,0:29:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you have a great app
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.81,0:29:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that's doing well in the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.61,0:29:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe you're just starting to
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.22,0:29:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,think of creating one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.07,0:29:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, I think you'll come
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.02,0:29:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,away with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.30,0:29:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, our current app is optimized
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.65,0:29:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,for watchOS 3.2, but to give you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.99,0:29:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the full scope of where we've
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.95,0:29:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,been and how we got here, we
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.37,0:29:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,need to step all the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.48,0:29:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All the way back to watchOS 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.99,0:29:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And the app that we created for
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.40,0:29:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.93,0:29:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, when watchOS 1 was
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.63,0:29:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,released, well WWDC 2015 was
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.85,0:29:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,right around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.47,0:30:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And we were already preparing
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.64,0:30:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the iOS app for that year.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.50,0:30:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this app would let you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.84,0:30:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,browse the schedule, add
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.95,0:30:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,favorite sessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.03,0:30:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the maps to the venue,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.24,0:30:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,read news throughout the week,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.40,0:30:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and view streaming videos, or
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.15,0:30:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,videos from previous years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.85,0:30:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But, now it was time for us to
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.59,0:30:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,decide what contextually made
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.50,0:30:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,sense for the wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.90,0:30:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we had these 4 areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.24,0:30:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,First we had schedule, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.71,0:30:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,schedule was a no-brainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.33,0:30:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the most crucial piece
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.15,0:30:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of information that we could
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.39,0:30:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,provide at a glance to somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.81,0:30:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,on the go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.74,0:30:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, we had maps.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.73,0:30:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maps not so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.42,0:30:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're at the actual
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.71,0:30:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,conference, the venue is
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.24,0:30:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,typically one building with
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.67,0:30:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,multiple floors and different
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.29,0:30:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,rooms everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.62,0:30:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And to get through that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.15,0:30:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,experience on Apple Watch, well
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.31,0:30:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we felt that that was best
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.40,0:30:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,served through the iOS app.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.36,0:31:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And really, honestly, if you're
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.93,0:31:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,staring that iOS app at the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.46,0:31:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,conference, you could also look
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.18,0:31:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,up into the real world and see
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.02,0:31:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the signs around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.51,0:31:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's farfetched.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.38,0:31:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.36,0:31:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we had news.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.62,0:31:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the time being we
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.43,0:31:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,thought that news made sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.18,0:31:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We have critical information
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.85,0:31:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that we shared throughout the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.75,0:31:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,week, and so we wanted to make
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.63,0:31:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,sure that somebody had access to
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.24,0:31:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.84,0:31:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,More on that in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.01,0:31:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, we had videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.97,0:31:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And videos, we cut right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.81,0:31:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It just didn't seem to make
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.15,0:31:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,sense to have that long form
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.88,0:31:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,video on your wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.68,0:31:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you imagine holding your
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.12,0:31:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,wrist for 40 to 60 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.64,0:31:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The arm gets a lot more beefier
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.33,0:31:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,than the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.97,0:31:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we have these key areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.22,0:31:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's look at the original
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.73,0:31:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Photoshop mockup that we made
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.10,0:31:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,for Watch app.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.76,0:31:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see here that we
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.86,0:31:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,actually took the schedule and
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.28,0:31:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we broke it down into three
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.90,0:31:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,distinct areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.26,0:32:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We had sessions, labs and
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.25,0:32:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.62,0:32:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And we also had the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.16,0:32:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, why did we break the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.46,0:32:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,schedule part?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.80,0:32:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there was a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.49,0:32:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,information to get across.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.48,0:32:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean at the beginning of the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.58,0:32:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,week, you'd have over 100
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.73,0:32:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,sessions, and over 100 labs.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.46,0:32:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And we wanted to make sure that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.89,0:32:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,someone could get around
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.13,0:32:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,exploring all of that content
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.90,0:32:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,really easily and quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.36,0:32:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, full disclosure here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.23,0:32:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This should've sent up huge red
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.27,0:32:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,flags that we were putting way
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.21,0:32:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,too much information into the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.60,0:32:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch app experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.45,0:32:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We were trying to break apart
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.92,0:32:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,all this content so that you
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.65,0:32:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,could get in and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.01,0:32:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well we'll talk more about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.23,0:32:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I can definitely
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.40,0:32:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,sympathize that when you first
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.40,0:32:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,start creating apps for watchOS,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.01,0:32:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a whole different ballgame.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.03,0:32:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're used to creating these
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.31,0:32:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,deep, reach experiences for iOS
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.17,0:32:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and you start stripping things
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.64,0:32:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,away for a great Watch app
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.31,0:32:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,experience, but then you start
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.07,0:32:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,feeling like you're stripping
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.68,0:33:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,too much away.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.75,0:33:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's getting too minimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.80,0:33:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And you start feeling that maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.89,0:33:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you should add more features to
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.00,0:33:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,add "value" to that experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.43,0:33:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've learned over time that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.72,0:33:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that's just not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.38,0:33:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you first start out,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.09,0:33:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a tricky scenario to get
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.10,0:33:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,into.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.77,0:33:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we also had news.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.04,0:33:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.04,0:33:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,With news, we found taking that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.68,0:33:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,plan and actually implementing
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.83,0:33:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,it and walking around for a week
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.20,0:33:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,with it on our wrist, that you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.37,0:33:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,had these news items, but the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.43,0:33:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,items were a bit long.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.81,0:33:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we couldn't have just one
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.07,0:33:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,gigantic list of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.76,0:33:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we actually needed to tap on
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.50,0:33:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,news, get to a list of news
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.31,0:33:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,items, then you tap on one, and
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.28,0:33:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,go into the details, where then
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.46,0:33:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you had all this text that you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.63,0:33:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,would scroll through.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.83,0:33:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And just the whole process of
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.21,0:33:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,going in that navigation
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.73,0:33:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,structure and back out to get to
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.55,0:33:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,your sessions, it was just
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.80,0:33:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,taking too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.21,0:33:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we actually decided before
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.13,0:33:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,release to even cut that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.74,0:34:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here's what we actually
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.97,0:34:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,shipped for watchOS 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.66,0:34:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We shipped the sessions, labs
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.89,0:34:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.43,0:34:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if I were Doug right now I
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.19,0:34:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,would say is this legible?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.50,0:34:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Is it concise?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.77,0:34:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it wasn't as concise as it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.47,0:34:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,could have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.90,0:34:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we needed to learn from that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.27,0:34:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.90,0:34:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we had some built-in
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.52,0:34:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,analytics to see where people
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.00,0:34:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,were landing and what area of
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.05,0:34:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the app that they really valued
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.91,0:34:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to make it really personal for
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.64,0:34:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.75,0:34:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And we found that they loved
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.92,0:34:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,this list of favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.11,0:34:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even from this list, we had
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.12,0:34:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,where you could tap on one of
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.32,0:34:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,these favorites and then it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.00,0:34:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,would give you more detailed
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.10,0:34:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,information; like the session
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.79,0:34:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,description.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.05,0:34:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And you could use the force
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.32,0:34:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,touch menu to favorite or
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.83,0:34:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,unfavorite a session.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.55,0:34:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But, what we found was that that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.59,0:34:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,process was taking too long, and
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.61,0:35:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,not a lot of people were using
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.14,0:35:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.84,0:35:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all using that list
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.62,0:35:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,right in the middle, because it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.06,0:35:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,was the things they cared about
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.71,0:35:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was really quick to
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.16,0:35:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,glance at.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.94,0:35:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean we now know, as of
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.31,0:35:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,watchOS 3 that really great
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.15,0:35:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,tasks on Apple Watch take about
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.93,0:35:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,2 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.60,0:35:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And for a non-nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.77,0:35:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,non-jittery person it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.52,0:35:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,about 2 seconds to say 2
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.97,0:35:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.26,0:35:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But, this whole process of going
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.42,0:35:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,down the navigation stack and
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.94,0:35:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,coming back up, it was actually
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.16,0:35:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,taking more like 5 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.31,0:35:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was just too long of an
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.76,0:35:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.58,0:35:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did we learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.02,0:35:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, watchOS 1 taught us that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.01,0:35:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we really needed to identify
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.82,0:35:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,what was most essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.45,0:35:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Find that single feature.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.76,0:35:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That one thing that you can
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.25,0:35:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,provide for the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.72,0:35:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.42,0:35:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we moved from watchOS 1 and
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.39,0:35:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.24,0:36:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And we went to watchOS 2 the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.65,0:36:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.57,0:36:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And we needed to do one key
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.09,0:36:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,thing in watchOS 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.50,0:36:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We needed to focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.44,0:36:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.84,0:36:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We really needed to focus on the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.74,0:36:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,feature set.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.94,0:36:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We needed to focus on the person
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.58,0:36:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and what they wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.98,0:36:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We needed to hone in on those
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.43,0:36:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,principles that Doug has spoken
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.23,0:36:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,about.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.18,0:36:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And we needed to re-ask
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.37,0:36:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,ourselves, what do people really
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.64,0:36:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,want on their wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.44,0:36:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But not just anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.44,0:36:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do people really want from
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.62,0:36:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the WWDC app on their wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.39,0:36:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.99,0:36:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That one piece of information
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.58,0:36:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that we can provide them?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.82,0:36:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we knew from feedback that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.03,0:36:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,they really loved the glance in
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.97,0:36:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,watchOS 1 because it showed them
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.16,0:36:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,this concise view of what was
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.06,0:36:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.84,0:36:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What was upcoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.97,0:36:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And they really liked that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.61,0:36:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we knew that we needed to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.70,0:37:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,provide the schedule in some
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.35,0:37:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of way, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.65,0:37:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we looked at what we were
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.84,0:37:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,offering here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.72,0:37:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We had sessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.21,0:37:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We had labs, and we had
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.58,0:37:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.60,0:37:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as I said it was a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.13,0:37:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,content if you wanted to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.81,0:37:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,explore.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.05,0:37:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we decided maybe we should
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.82,0:37:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,just take sessions and labs out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.56,0:37:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should go all the way
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.75,0:37:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and just make it very, very
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.07,0:37:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,personal of an experience and
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.23,0:37:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,really focus on favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.57,0:37:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We had this master detail
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.11,0:37:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,navigation structure and so we
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.67,0:37:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at it spread out, and we
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.57,0:37:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,just said, well this seems
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.57,0:37:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,pretty straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.06,0:37:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take this
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.94,0:37:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,navigation structure and just
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.55,0:37:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,condense it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.28,0:37:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Get that list of favorites that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.52,0:37:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.80,0:37:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is what we shipped for
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.12,0:37:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,watchOS 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.46,0:37:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We went down to only favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.70,0:37:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, not only did we go down
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.85,0:37:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.89,0:37:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We also made it so that it was
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.91,0:38:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,only favorites from now until
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.56,0:38:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the end of the conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.14,0:38:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this was something that we
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.68,0:38:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,don't even provide in the iOS
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.89,0:38:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,app.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.35,0:38:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a feature that is only
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.67,0:38:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,on Apple Watch, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.21,0:38:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,On iOS you can actually look at
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.28,0:38:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,your previous favorites from the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.72,0:38:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,week, because you can get that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.28,0:38:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,rich experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.24,0:38:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You can explore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.85,0:38:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But on the Watch, it really
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.67,0:38:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,makes more sense to just have
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.17,0:38:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,what's now and what's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.16,0:38:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing to note here is a
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.33,0:38:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,small detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.06,0:38:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In watchOS 1, our table section
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.09,0:38:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,headers above sessions, were
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.93,0:38:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,dates, and time ranges.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.10,0:38:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not very glanceable.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.82,0:38:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what we did was we actually
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.22,0:38:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,made this more legible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.23,0:38:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing what one word, the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.30,0:38:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,placement of one word can do for
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.54,0:38:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,your apps experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.32,0:38:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see here that we used
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.45,0:38:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,words like now and upcoming to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.47,0:38:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,show you what was actually going
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.98,0:38:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.42,0:39:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You could quickly glance at the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.86,0:39:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,app and know, oh okay, I can't
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.01,0:39:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,go for coffee right now because
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.70,0:39:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually supposed to be in
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.70,0:39:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,this other session.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.95,0:39:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, I don't have one upcoming
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.80,0:39:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,until further out, so I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.96,0:39:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's these small details that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.82,0:39:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,add to that personal experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.58,0:39:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, in watchOS 2, we took full
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.64,0:39:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,advantage of complications,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.39,0:39:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,which were introduced in watchOS
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.99,0:39:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,2.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.63,0:39:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That timeliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.51,0:39:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And if people wanted to have
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.62,0:39:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,their favorites on their Watch
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.88,0:39:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,face, they could enable the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.78,0:39:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,large slot on the modular Watch
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.71,0:39:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,face and take advantage of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.04,0:39:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But we also wanted them to be
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.69,0:39:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,able to get to our content no
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.60,0:39:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,matter what kind of Watch face
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.45,0:39:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,they used.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.53,0:39:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And we went through a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.74,0:39:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,struggle of like, do we provide
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.55,0:39:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,something that just launches
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.88,0:39:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,them to our app, or what can we
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.73,0:39:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,provide in these smaller areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.49,0:39:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And really when it came down to
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.15,0:39:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it, we found that with the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.86,0:39:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,information that we had, there
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.05,0:39:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't anything that was
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.19,0:40:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,amazingly valuable in that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.77,0:40:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,constrained, confined amount of
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.62,0:40:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,space.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.68,0:40:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, we actually went ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.36,0:40:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and used launchers.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.17,0:40:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But we made some custom ones for
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.61,0:40:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the different slot styles, so
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.55,0:40:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that you know it blended in a
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.37,0:40:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,little bit more nicely with the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.68,0:40:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,experience, and we did this for
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.19,0:40:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,two reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.27,0:40:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The first reason I spoke about
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.85,0:40:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,was that preference factor,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.72,0:40:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.61,0:40:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they use a different
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.99,0:40:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of watch face?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.03,0:40:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to allow them to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.44,0:40:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and still have quick access to
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.15,0:40:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the content.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.68,0:40:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But, we did this for a second
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.42,0:40:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,reason as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.30,0:40:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,App discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.48,0:40:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you only support one or a few
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.60,0:40:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,type of complication styles,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.28,0:40:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,then if they use a different
