Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.25,0:40:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,complication.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.40,0:41:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we wanted to be
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.40,0:41:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,discoverable.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.56,0:41:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And fit in to how they use Apple
