Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.53,0:41:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,points by 18 points at 2x,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.35,0:41:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's a retina screen,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.51,0:41:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.32,0:41:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here for watchOS 2 what did we
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.70,0:41:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.79,0:41:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we learned that you really
