Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.74,0:41:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,means the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.23,0:41:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.71,0:41:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so now we go to watchOS 2
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.19,0:41:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to watchOS 3, and where our app
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.45,0:41:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,currently is.
