Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.79,0:42:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in my team, and they first saw
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.78,0:42:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,it and they're like oh, this is
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.75,0:42:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.77,0:42:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And they were really excited and
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.81,0:42:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,they're like yeah, WWDC is
