Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.11,0:42:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch face.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.33,0:42:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was like great.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.61,0:42:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.48,0:42:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But the point is that it adhered
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.85,0:42:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to whatever your preference is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.87,0:42:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you want that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.23,0:43:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,experience to be, you can still
