Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.64,0:43:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.40,0:43:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing that we did was,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.02,0:43:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we made use of background app
