Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.00,0:43:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.16,0:43:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.31,0:43:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said just moving to the
