Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.39,0:43:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,taking advantage of it is just
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.39,0:43:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as important.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.51,0:43:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you may think that this is
