Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.36,0:44:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,future.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.55,0:44:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,With the announcement this week
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.12,0:44:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of watchOS 4, we're excited as
