Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.36,0:44:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,legible.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.17,0:44:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it more concise so that it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.60,0:44:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is only one session at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.85,0:45:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is kind of what I put
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.74,0:45:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,together so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.29,0:45:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I found that we can actually
