Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.80,0:47:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,valuable that would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.93,0:47:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Or if it should be like a
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.98,0:47:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,rolling 24-hour window or
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.11,0:47:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.98,0:47:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean we're still continuing to
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.26,0:47:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,iterate, just like you do on
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.58,0:47:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,your apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.71,0:47:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, we'll see where we
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.87,0:47:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,land for next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.95,0:47:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we went version by version,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.34,0:47:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are somethings that
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.82,0:47:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,are evergreen on Apple Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.32,0:47:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Take for instance, notification.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.62,0:47:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Notifications are one of the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.63,0:47:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,greatest pieces of Apple Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.49,0:47:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean definitely for me when
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.15,0:47:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,people ask me why I love Apple
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.96,0:47:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch so much, that's usually
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.72,0:47:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the one thing that I rave about.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.96,0:47:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you get these
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.40,0:47:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,notifications, and they're
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.65,0:47:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,information coming to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.22,0:47:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.62,0:47:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's relevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.89,0:47:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's contextual.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.19,0:47:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.08,0:47:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we have notifications like
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.98,0:47:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,these.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.33,0:47:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Take for instance CARROT weather
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.07,0:47:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,in the US.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.56,0:47:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I set up in the app to get
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.92,0:47:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,tomorrow's forecast every night
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.96,0:48:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,at 9 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.50,0:48:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And what I get is the app sends
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.62,0:48:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,a notification based on my
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.21,0:48:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,location and it takes over the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.26,0:48:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,screen and shows me in a very
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.33,0:48:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,beautiful format the high, the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.85,0:48:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,low, possible precipitation for
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.09,0:48:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.92,0:48:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And all I have to do is glance
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.79,0:48:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,at that, and then I know when I
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.60,0:48:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,wake up the next morning how I
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.07,0:48:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,need to dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.78,0:48:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How I need to prepare for my
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.05,0:48:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,day.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.59,0:48:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just coming to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.18,0:48:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.64,0:48:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, a lot of notifications that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.82,0:48:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I get, they look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.43,0:48:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the default.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.04,0:48:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the default looks nice and
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.39,0:48:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,all but also look at this text.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.20,0:48:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It says check out the latest
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.65,0:48:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,news update.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.95,0:48:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.53,0:48:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I have to go to the app and
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.25,0:48:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,check out the news update.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.70,0:48:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,OK is it relevant to me, I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.68,0:48:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.09,0:48:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess. But with only about
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.47,0:48:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,four minutes worth of work, what
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.98,0:48:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you can do is you can open your
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.46,0:48:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,storyboard in your project.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.56,0:49:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use the colors of your
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.47,0:49:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,app and apply those.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.18,0:49:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can apply them like this
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.54,0:49:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to your apps name, to the sash,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.20,0:49:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.42,0:49:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use spacing, textiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.37,0:49:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it more legible.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.72,0:49:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it more visually
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.75,0:49:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.13,0:49:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll also notice here that
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.29,0:49:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,there's more text.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.28,0:49:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So that right when I get the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.47,0:49:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,notification, I know what it's
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.01,0:49:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,about.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.25,0:49:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, pay attention here, because
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.82,0:49:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,this text for the notification
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.01,0:49:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is actually custom written for
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.74,0:49:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the notifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.13,0:49:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for the notification
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.33,0:49:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,payload.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.28,0:49:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the news in the app could
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.06,0:49:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,be longer, include more detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.11,0:49:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the gist.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.46,0:49:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the important piece of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.31,0:49:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,relevant information that we
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.69,0:49:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,want you to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.13,0:49:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Four minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.34,0:49:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.27,0:49:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If we work our way backwards, we
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.22,0:49:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,can see the short look
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.40,0:49:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,notification.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.41,0:49:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this is what displays on
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.37,0:49:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Watch, right when you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.04,0:49:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that haptic and raise your
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.38,0:49:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,wrist, when a notification
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.66,0:50:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.92,0:50:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It has your app icon, bit and
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.66,0:50:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.05,0:50:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And it has your app name.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.42,0:50:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, notice the app name is in
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.93,0:50:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,white.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.31,0:50:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, this is the default.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.49,0:50:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But with one line of code in
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.00,0:50:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,your payload, you can use the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.06,0:50:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,title key value pair and what
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.57,0:50:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,this allows you to do is provide
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.40,0:50:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,some more context as to what
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.15,0:50:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,this notification is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.21,0:50:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, what happens is this is
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.11,0:50:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,what it will look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.38,0:50:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When it arrives on your wrist,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.72,0:50:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it will have your beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.25,0:50:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,icon, but it will also have that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.28,0:50:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,title string between the icon
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.55,0:50:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and your app's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.21,0:50:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, immediately, I can see
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.84,0:50:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is this relevant to my
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.96,0:50:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.99,0:50:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I look at this later?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.70,0:50:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm playing with my kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.19,0:50:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,or I'm in a meeting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.57,0:50:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other thing that you'll
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.79,0:50:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,notice is that the app name is
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.89,0:50:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,in the primary tint color for
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.84,0:50:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the app.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.78,0:50:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it takes on more visual
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.31,0:50:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,sensibilities of your app.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.81,0:51:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, truly four minutes and one
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.79,0:51:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,line of additional text, can
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.05,0:51:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,take you from default
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.54,0:51:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,notifications, to much more
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.47,0:51:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,relevant, contextual, visually
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.17,0:51:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,interesting notifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.93,0:51:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, so we've spoken about a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.65,0:51:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,today and planning is key.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.81,0:51:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Really think about that process
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.48,0:51:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of planning and designing your
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.38,0:51:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.56,0:51:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you this process
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.62,0:51:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,should actually be the majority
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.96,0:51:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of the entire development cycle
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.39,0:51:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,for your Watch app.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.75,0:51:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The implementation will be a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.88,0:51:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,smaller timeframe.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.60,0:51:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then all the planning and design
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.39,0:51:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to really make a great
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.54,0:51:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.70,0:51:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Also. try to start simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.28,0:51:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see, even we made that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.00,0:51:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.73,0:51:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought we were starting
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.84,0:51:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,simple, but we still had more
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.21,0:51:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that we could do to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.76,0:51:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,concise, to make it more
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.23,0:51:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.19,0:51:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about that in your own
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.23,0:51:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.24,0:52:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, iterate, refine.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.90,0:52:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When the OS moves up to another
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.51,0:52:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,version, take advantage of what
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.62,0:52:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you can, but don't feel like you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.62,0:52:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,need to completely reinvent your
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.58,0:52:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,app just because it's the next
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.70,0:52:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,version.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.89,0:52:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For more information please
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.14,0:52:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,check out this link.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.12,0:52:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got links to our
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.56,0:52:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,resources, the watchOS human
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.24,0:52:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,interface guidelines and much
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.18,0:52:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,more.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.57,0:52:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There are also some related
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.58,0:52:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,sessions you should definitely
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.04,0:52:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,check out if you haven't, such
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.83,0:52:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,as "What's New in watchOS," you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.43,0:52:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,can see what you can take
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.70,0:52:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,advantage of in watchOS 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.30,0:52:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.52,0:52:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
